{"tid":271201,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"基士文：如果現在離開馬體會，是一個卑鄙舉動。","createTime":"2017-06-05T01:40:36.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-05T12:30:46.000Z","uid":30040,"like":13,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"61c0824a418139a3cdd755cb4a055fb1d8e14064","tid":271201,"uid":30040,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-05T01:40:36.000Z","msg":"馬體會前鋒基士文本週日在接受T&eacute;l&eacute;foot採訪時，宣佈自己下賽季仍會留在馬德里體育會，並表示在馬體會遭受轉會禁令的處罰時，在這個時候離開會是一個卑鄙的行為。<br />\n「關於我未來的那些問題讓人夠煩了。國際體育仲裁法庭的裁決已經出來了，馬體會不能引援。我與體育顧問艾力克-奧拉茲一起決定留下來。這是球會一個艱難的時刻。如果現在離開，會是一個卑鄙的舉動。我和高層們談過了，我們下賽季會重新出發。」<br />\n對於馬體會不能在今夏引進拉卡傑特一事，基士文為此感到遺憾：「這對他來說是個遺憾，讓人難過。我希望他在九月至十二月這段時間做出一些不錯的事。十二月時，我們會再來打探的。」"},{"pid":"b603897c98e96f8cb286c64738942e878396d907","tid":271201,"uid":47303,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-05T01:43:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9eb6ff57a61462d737e61960ce4b8996043d12a9","tid":271201,"uid":9668,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-05T01:44:32.000Z","msg":"球壇做君子有幾多個有好下場<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6ff8f99dc9f5f1b2b36330287d78077910f1bd8d","tid":271201,"uid":5922,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-05T01:45:05.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"13b7d0c2d07ac081653a2a0d6630eae315abb186","tid":271201,"uid":4917,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-05T01:45:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/06/05/094523_7621b0798f52461ffabe0f7832535feb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F06%2F05%2F094523_7621b0798f52461ffabe0f7832535feb.jpg&h=ba87f7f8&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"317fe9478eb963c9e3d0029e120ce710d863716e","tid":271201,"uid":92603,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-05T01:45:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>球壇做君子有幾多個有好下場<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wond